reviewText: Okay, this need more planning, some good highlights, maybe they should have gather highlights from games that didn't get the greatest attention. Still a good DVD to add to your collection if you are a fan of football.

I got this dvd because I am a huge Reggie Bush fan.  I wanted some of his games on dvd.  The dvd is okay I just wanted more games.  They condense the games to mostly highlights which is okay but not want I was looking for.
